My young daughter is learning to read, and I wrote this simple
Flash app as a practice aid.

To get help with a word, click the Say button (or press S or the
space bar).

To go to the next word, click the Next button (or press N or Enter).

The files words/*.mp3 are derivative works of pronunciations from
Wiktionary (http://en.wiktionary.org/), which are dual-licensed
under both the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 Unported
License and the GNU Free Documentation License.

See it live:

  http://gbacon.blogspot.com/2009/07/just-for-you-madeline.html
